<A>__{looking increasingly twitchy as he approaches the cross girder. he slips a hand into the pocket of his topcoat, whirls suddenly and brings up his .38 automatic, firing three quick shots at the penguin. the shots ricochet loudly off the umbrella which happens to be a bulletproof job. the penguin lifts his brolly; fire spits out of the shaft and tiptree staggers backward. shot in the chest. he spins into a steel upright and topples, face forward, onto the electrified third rail frying himself in a shower of sparks. the smoke is still clearing when the catwoman drops to the tracks. the penguin rushes to her side to check tiptree for signs of life.}
